<section class="section-summary pad text-center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 columns">
      <h3>Xonotic is an addictive arena-style first person shooter with crisp
          movement and a wide array of weapons. It combines intuitive mechanics
          with in-your-face action to elevate your heart rate.
          Xonotic will always be free to play and modify under the
          <a href="https://www.gnu.org/copyleft/" title="copyleft licensing">copyleft</a>
          <a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt" title="The GPLv3+ license">GPLv3+</a> license.</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="screenshots row text-center">
    <div class="small-3 columns">
